  "body": "When launching the validator client with three validator keys, one had a password that was not provided correctly and the validator failed with:\r\n\r\n`ERROR main: could not get private key: could not decrypt key with given passphrase`\r\n\r\nThe ideal behavior is that the validator would continue to validate for keys with the correct passphrase while aggressively reporting the warning for the key(s) with incorrect passwords. One bad key should not stop the whole show.",
